{"id":"4370ac58-20f4-4b09-aa0c-2805b5a313e5","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>texts | </strong>“cUM to ger mw m :’((“ you’re receiving drunken texts from your ex-boyfriend on a week night</p><hr><p>☁️💬☁️</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">𝝑𝝔 </span></mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">Scenario </span></mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">𝝑𝝔</span></mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">It’s been a few months since the breakup, and after you threatened to block his number, Satoru has stopped trying to call you.</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">You were glad to think he moved on, but really he never left square 1. Which you realize after he sends you an incoherent text and an address.</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffefed; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 169, 180)\">art credit: i couldn’t find the artist please tell me if you know!!!</span></mark></strong></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7bf53a3-ecba-43e3-a108-bd699c8806fc_714df7dc-1733-438a-b511-97b11af1add0.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); caret-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; width: 302px; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"false\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffefed; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 169, 180)\">☁️happy 300!!!! ☁️</span></mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">🤍</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">𝝑𝝔 skip to </span></mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">Notes </span></mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">for bot info! 𝝑𝝔</span></mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">.•*:｡☁️ 💬𓍼ֶָ֢⊹</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">I didn’t expect us to get here this fast 😭 but I’m so happy we’re here 🤍</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">I think what I plan to do for now is to make a multibot for every 200😚I hope that’s alright🤍</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">this bot is a part 2 of the first bot I made that ever really got attention (which was a joke-bot but bare with me), which I’ve been meaning to make for awhile due to suggestions for it 😭</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\">to look back on my first 10 or so bots I get so embarrassed sometimes 🙉 🙈 tbh I think about taking them down a LOT but I think it’s worth having them up because it shows a lot of my progress and growth or whatever 😫 also I don’t want people to randomly lose their ability to use it, still embarrassing though 🌚 I hope people aren’t still finding my account through my McDonalds Gojo bot 🌚</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-ali","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"b7bf53a3-ecba-43e3-a108-bd699c8806fc_1d12dc8c-8b16-49ca-83dd-1092fd9fa098.webp","creator":"toovaeloe","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":2118,"messages":24323,"created_at":"2024-08-10T20:27:01.442608+00:00"}